# Exclude third-party / library code from GitHub's language stats.
# These are not authored by this project, so they shouldn't count
# toward the repo's detected language.

PhysicsEngine/PhysicsEngine/lib/**  linguist-vendored
packages/**                         linguist-vendored

# Treat the project's own headers as C++ (Linguist sometimes guesses C).
*.h linguist-language=C++
